nodes.text: A chef or cook was an individual who prepared food. Dexter Jettster, the owner of Dex's Diner on Coruscant, cooked food for his customers. Strono Tuggs, a male Artiodac, served as a chef in Takodana Castle, and another Artiodac chef was staffed in the crew of a young smuggler. A human chef was known to operate from within the Haven, a refuge for defenseless citizens created by the Spectres.
